headline: UnitedHealth Group (UNH) CEO Buys $25 Million Worth of Company Stock
summary: The Form 4 filing by UnitedHealth Group (NYSE:UNH) shows that the new CEO, Stephen Hemsley, acquired $25 million worth of company shares at an average of $288.57 a piece on Friday, 16th May 2025.
